Napieralski Says Poland’s Left Sees Signs of Fiscal ‘Collapse’

-- B y   D a v i d   M c Q u a i d
-- 
2011-09-28T10:33:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/napieralski-says-poland-s-left-sees-signs-of-fiscal-collapse-.html
Poland’s public finances are
showing signs of “collapse” under Prime Minister Donald Tusk’s
government,  Grzegorz Napieralski , the leader of the opposition
Democratic  Left Alliance , said today in Warsaw.  Napieralski was speaking in parliament during a public
meeting with Finance Minister Jacek Rostowski ahead of the
country’s Oct. 9 general elections.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David McQuaid at 
 dmcquaid1@bloomberg.net  